The paper discusses the design and analysis of mixed-signal neuromorphic processors, which falls under the category of computational neuroscience (cs.NE). The use of advanced process technology and the challenges it poses for analog design suggest that the paper may also belong to the categories of electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET), architecture (cs.AR), electromagnetics (cs.EM), and computer engineering (cs.CE).
